Twisty Passages - A simple rogue-like dungeon crawler
Copyright (C) 2020  Elliot Dronebarger

Dependencies:
- SDL2
- SDL2_ttf
- yaml-cpp (submodule)

To compile, you will need:
- SDL2 headers and library
- The yaml-cpp submodule

Building:
git submodule update --init
mkdir -p ext/yaml-cpp/build && cd ext/yaml-cpp/build
cmake ..
make

cd ../../..
mkdir -p build && cd build
cmake ..
make
